1
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:44,170
[A Moment But Forever]

2
00:01:45,110 --> 00:01:47,150
[Episode 18]

3
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:48,920
Here.

4
00:01:50,539 --> 00:01:51,509
This wine is really good.

5
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,710
We have wine and meat here.

6
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,860
What's the special occasion today?

7
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,610
Of course, it's the day we're starting to renovate the house.

8
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:56,509
No.

9
00:01:57,850 --> 00:02:00,690
Today is the day of our engagement.

10
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,600
So, the date is set?

11
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:04,680
Yes.

12
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:05,560
Today,

13
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,950
I went to Liu the Blind for a fortune-telling.

14
00:02:06,970 --> 00:02:08,960
The 9th of next month is an auspicious day.

15
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,430
So I plan to

16
00:02:11,770 --> 00:02:13,050
marry Yunniang on that day.

17
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:14,750
That's wonderful!

18
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,710
Isn't it just a few days away?

19
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:17,790
That's right.

20
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,680
Yes.

21
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,590
Just a few days.

22
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:21,800
Before we start,

23
00:02:21,890 --> 00:02:24,600
I'd like to say something.

24
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:29,310
I have no father, no mother,

25
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,120
and my foster father, my only family, has passed away.

26
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,520
Yunniang's family is also gone.

27
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,470
Although you've only just arrived recently,

28
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:36,590
and we had

29
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,579
some misunderstandings when we first met,

30
00:02:39,850 --> 00:02:41,890
over these past few days,

31
00:02:42,010 --> 00:02:43,520
we've gotten along like long-time friends.

32
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:45,240
Since everyone's here today,

33
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:47,430
I'd like to ask you to be my witnesses.

34
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,400
Okay!

35
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,630
Yunniang.

36
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,840
Yunniang.

37
00:03:00,490 --> 00:03:03,000
From now on,

38
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,190
we'll be living together.

39
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,630
Thank you for not minding my poverty.

40
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:06,990
I know

41
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,310
I have

42
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:10,120
all sorts of flaws.

43
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:12,280
But I have

44
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,630
a true heart that

45
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:15,240
I'm not afraid to show you.

46
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,280
I won't say much about the future.

47
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,280
You'll see for yourself.

48
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:21,030
I will definitely work hard to protect you,

49
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:21,750
to stay by your side,

50
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,400
and take care of you for the rest of my life.

51
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,470
Yunniang,

52
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:27,310
if you have any requests for me,

53
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:28,240
just say them.

54
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,430
I'm sure I can fulfill them.

55
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,360
I don't have any requests for you.

56
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:32,630
It's just that the last time,

57
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:33,840
when I married that unlucky guy,

58
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,360
he passed away before I even

59
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,360
stepped into his house.

60
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,710
Really disappointing.

61
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:38,990
He left me a widow for no reason.

62
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,320
So,

63
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:42,360
I only have one request for you.

64
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:44,230
Pei Jiu,

65
00:03:44,579 --> 00:03:45,910
you must live a long life

66
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,079
and stay with me through this lifetime.

67
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,030
Okay.

68
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,800
Let's all have a drink together!

69
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,630
Come on.

70
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,630
Wish you a long life and a happy marriage.

71
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:57,800
May you have children soon.

72
00:03:58,190 --> 00:03:59,000
May you stay safe.

73
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,450
Thank you, everyone.

74
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,400
Cool!

75
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:04,910
It's really good!

76
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:05,630
Jiu,

77
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,560
today, you should have

78
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,710
invited your master.

79
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,150
Where is Mr. Yuan?

80
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:11,590
Yuanzhong has already eaten,

81
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,280
so he's not coming.

82
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,950
How about I make a new set of furniture

83
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:20,950
as a gift for you two?

84
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:23,000
Tables, chairs,

85
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,310
and baby beds—

86
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:26,040
just tell me anything you like,

87
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,800
and I can make it

88
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,680
for you.

89
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,360
That's wonderful! Thank you.

90
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,070
Come on, come on.

91
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:31,940
Let's have a drink!

92
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,250
If I don't drink you under the table today,

93
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,120
I won't call myself Kai Shan anymore.

94
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,040
Congratulations.

95
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:36,430
If you put it that way,

96
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,720
do you think you can outdrink me?

97
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:49,480
Mr. Tanghua, have you ever been to Yandu?

98
00:04:50,310 --> 00:04:51,120
Never.

99
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,950
This is my first time seeing

100
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,800
such a big, bustling city of the human race.

101
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:56,000
Yandu...

102
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:58,310
seems like a city that appeared out of nowhere.

103
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,560
Appeared out of nowhere?

104
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,310
That's right.

105
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,950
When it first appeared in the history books of the human race,

106
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,480
it was already a city.

107
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,480
According to my people's historical records,

108
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,480
this place was originally surrounded by steep mountains,

109
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,560
with dangerous terrain,

110
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,120
and was a desolate area.

111
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,630
But one day,

112
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,310
a passing merchant caravan

113
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,240
suddenly discovered

114
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,720
that a city had appeared here.

115
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,680
The news of this city's appearance

116
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,120
quickly spread.

117
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,800
While the world was shocked,

118
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,630
everyone wanted to claim it for themselves.

119
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:27,870
Back then,

120
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:29,270
Chenshang Kingdom and Qiong Kingdom

121
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:31,120
fought a long and drawn-out war

122
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,070
over the ownership

123
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,510
of Yandu,

124
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:36,270
but neither side could claim victory.

125
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:38,390
It wasn't until the war between gods and demons,

126
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:41,240
when the flames of war from the Divine Realm spread to the Mortal Realm,

127
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,560
that it came to an end.

128
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,870
After the Battle of Pinghu,

129
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:46,120
the human race finally realized

130
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,430
the importance of unity.

131
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,560
Although people are still divided into different countries,

132
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,950
there is little conflict now,

133
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,510
and Yandu has become completely independent,

134
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:55,159
turning into

135
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:56,720
the bustling city of trade it is today.

136
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,480
The Scholar's Wall,

137
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,920
tool shops, and the Craftsmanship Museum

138
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,240
are all unique features of Yandu.

139
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,190
You really know a lot

140
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:04,400
about Yandu.

141
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:06,360
I was born here, so naturally, I know.

142
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:09,870
Are you here in Yandu on business?

143
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:12,000
No, just sightseeing.

144
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,950
I heard that since the Craftsmanship Museum

145
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:17,310
came under the management of the Merchant Association,

146
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,190
they've started charging an entrance fee.

147
00:06:19,590 --> 00:06:20,420
I was thinking of

148
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:21,860
going there in the next few days to take a look.

149
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:24,480
How much is the entrance fee?

150
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,590
I don't know about that.

151
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,070
These

152
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:29,240
are usually handled by Jiuguang and others.

153
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,480
Right.

154
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,310
Sir, you have a noble background

155
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,560
and refined taste.

156
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:36,800
How could you care about such trivial matters?

157
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:39,360
I heard that you are fond of poetry and calligraphy.

158
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,800
It is said that

159
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,630
when Master Xu passed by the Scholar's Wall,

160
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,680
he also left an inscription on it.

161
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,270
Have you seen it?

162
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:48,540
There are so many inscriptions on the Scholar's Wall.

163
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,470
I didn't notice it.

164
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:58,640
Sir, why do you seem so guarded around me?

165
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,120
Could it be...

166
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,160
I just don't understand

167
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:10,390
why I didn't notice a girl like you

168
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,950
when you were interested in me.

169
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,310
Your heart wasn't with me,

170
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,230
so of course, you didn't see me.

171
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:20,510
Now I've noticed you,

172
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,840
but your heart is no longer with me.

173
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,070
Before you came,

174
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,560
I had already visited that restaurant for 7 consecutive days.

175
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,510
I joked with Jiuguang,

176
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:34,000
saying I was fishing.

177
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,680
During those 7 days,

178
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,750
I thought of several possibilities.

179
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,270
I even thought that the one coming

180
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,680
could be a War Demon

181
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,680
or some kind of warlock from the martial world.

182
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,630
But I never expected

183
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,360
that it would be you—

184
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:49,159
Young Mistress Dai of Yandu City.

185
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,800
How...

186
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,830
How did I know?

187
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:56,040
You hide your identity but not your name,

188
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,390
so it's easy to inquire about you.

189
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:59,000
In Yandu City,

190
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,830
your name is well known

191
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,270
even to children.

192
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,870
I'm not your enemy.

193
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:03,720
You are not?

194
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,390
I don't think so.

195
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:07,480
Back then, when the war first broke out,

196
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,120
my people charged into battle,

197
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:11,360
while the human race sat back and watched from the sidelines.

198
00:08:11,620 --> 00:08:13,010
I can never forget this grudge.

199
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,310
If it weren't for the War Demons later

200
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:16,310
launching a massive invasion of human cities,

201
00:08:16,590 --> 00:08:18,470
burning and killing fiercely

202
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,920
the human race wouldn't have sought an alliance with my people.

203
00:08:20,950 --> 00:08:21,720
But our two races

204
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,830
did ally in the end.

205
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,870
So what?

206
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,950
If the roles were reversed now,

207
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,510
and the War Demons were the ones

208
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,750
hiding and barely surviving,

209
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,930
what choice would the human race make?

210
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,240
Don't you believe

211
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,960
in moderation and balance the most?

212
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,320
Humans are truly strange.

213
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,909
Though weak,

214
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,440
you still persist and thrive.

215
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,080
When there's no external enemy,

216
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,000
you fight among yourselves,

217
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,000
destroying the peace and prosperity with your own hands.

218
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,440
But when an enemy appears,

219
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,320
you can immediately unite

220
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:52,510
and create extraordinary miracles.

221
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,750
Over the past 60 years,

222
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,200
while the War Demons vanished without a trace,

223
00:08:55,870 --> 00:08:57,520
who has been

224
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,280
holding you together?

225
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,960
Humans are always wavering.

226
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:04,030
Now that the War Demons are returning,

227
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:05,910
you are wavering again,

228
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:07,170
aren't you?

229
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:08,200
So?

230
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,720
You suspect my people have colluded

231
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,320
with the remnants of the War Demons, don't you?

232
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,000
Shouldn't I?

233
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,560
If you want to disassociate yourselves from it,

234
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:16,030
just provide solid proof.

235
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,720
What's the deal with Lyu Yao?

236
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:19,650
And what about the Green Garden Trading House?

237
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:20,870
And the Wushuang Society?

238
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,150
Can you disassociate yourselves from all of them?

239
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:24,080
I can.

240
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,320
Trust me.

241
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:26,600
Trust you?

242
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:29,750
The Young Mistress of Yandu City,

243
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:32,010
with such noble status,

244
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,840
second only to the emperor,

245
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,080
is undoubtedly

246
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,200
the cream of the crop.

247
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:39,180
Yet this noble person

248
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,510
willingly went to Fangwai Mountain

249
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:43,180
and became a humble handmaiden,

250
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,440
remaining so for 10 years.

251
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,390
And it was actually

252
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,480
because of me.

253
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,750
Listen to yourself.

254
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,870
Which of these words is believable?

255
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,720
How do you expect me to believe that?

256
00:09:58,270 --> 00:09:59,240
I'm such a fool,

257
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:01,750
to come here full of guilt

258
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:03,660
over something like this.

259
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,840
It's truly laughable.

260
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,080
You can suspect

261
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,510
that my people are involved in this matter,

262
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,080
but you cannot doubt

263
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:15,910
my feelings for you

264
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,120
over the past few decades,

265
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,960
even though they no longer exist now.

266
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,030
You're right.

267
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:26,600
We are indeed good at clever planning.

268
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,910
Of course,

269
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,750
in your eyes,

270
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,270
it might just be scheming and trickery.

271
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,670
In my ten years on the mountain,

272
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,600
I've seen enough of your people

273
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:38,000
fighting to the death over conflicts,

274
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,120
and I've also seen

275
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,630
how you've struggled

276
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,060
and strived

277
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,330
in difficult situations.

278
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,510
Tanghua,

279
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,600
with how well I know you and how much attention I've paid to you,

280
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,360
if I wanted to harm you,

281
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:51,970
you would have been dead long ago.

282
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,200
This wine is really good.

283
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,870
I'll drink this again next time.

284
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:09,120
Of course.

285
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,320
Let me tell you,

286
