00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:19,030
I'd renovate this old house of mine.

573
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:19,950
Master, look.

574
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:21,900
That porch, those windows,

575
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:23,030
and the roof—

576
00:28:23,300 --> 00:28:24,410
they're all things I've recently renovated.

577
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,310
Master, let's go inside and have a seat.

578
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:28,680
Alright.

579
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,070
Master, please come in.

580
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:33,240
Once the new furniture is in place,

581
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:34,700
this house will look brand new.

582
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,400
Master, please have a seat.

583
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:43,680
How do you like it?

584
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:46,480
Not bad.

585
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:49,790
What's this?

586
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,310
Well, this house

587
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:52,200
just got renovated.

588
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,830
A new house should have a god's image hung up.

589
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:56,080
This is the image of the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain

590
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,480
I invited here.

591
00:28:58,550 --> 00:28:59,350
Master,

592
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,110
since you're here,

593
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:02,240
could you help me

594
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,160
figure out

595
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,350
where to hang this image?

596
00:29:04,550 --> 00:29:05,720
This Mute Lady of Wu Mountain

597
00:29:08,350 --> 00:29:09,880
has a lot of things with her.

598
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,240
Master.

599
00:29:12,550 --> 00:29:13,640
These are the Mute Goddess's

600
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,720
three magical treasures—

601
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:16,750
a divine whip that cannot be destroyed,

602
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:18,510
a phoenix that soars in the sky,

603
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:19,590
and

604
00:29:19,590 --> 00:29:21,350
a treasure bag that can carry all things.

605
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:30,510
Is this the thing you were in a hurry

606
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:31,440
to get back?

607
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:33,070
Exactly.

608
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:34,270
Thank you, Madam.

609
00:29:40,870 --> 00:29:42,150
So sharp.

610
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,750
You tried my dagger?

611
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:45,510
I meant your eyes.

612
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:48,750
When you were lying down,

613
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:50,180
you looked so gentle and harmless.

614
00:29:50,470 --> 00:29:53,230
But now that you've woken up, your eyes are like a drawn sword.

615
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,070
Young people,

616
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:55,720
showing your sharpness and aggressiveness

617
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,400
isn't always a good thing.

618
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:01,790
Thank you for your advice, Madam.

619
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:03,590
And thank you for taking care of me these days.

620
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,400
Looking after you is not quite right.

621
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,750
After all, I was paid for it.

622
00:30:06,790 --> 00:30:08,400
If you really want to thank me,

623
00:30:08,490 --> 00:30:09,860
leave here as soon as possible.

624
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:12,070
I've been in business for a long time,

625
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:13,620
so I've developed a keen eye for people.

626
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:16,160
I'm never wrong about people.

627
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:18,070
Once you're healed, leave quickly

628
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:18,720
and don't bring trouble

629
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:19,830
to my inn.

630
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,590
Tanyin.

631
00:30:32,350 --> 00:30:33,400
What are you carrying?

632
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:35,640
It's some food for the patient.

633
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,400
Patient?

634
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:37,920
We don't have any patients here.

635
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:39,110
It's for the person inside.

636
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:41,160
That guy has woken up,

637
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,540
so he's no longer a patient.

638
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:43,920
Aren't you busy today?

639
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:45,310
It's alright.

640
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:46,070
Then I'll send...

641
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:47,410
I've told you there's no need to check on him.

642
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:48,590
You're a young girl,

643
00:30:48,590 --> 00:30:49,510
and it's not appropriate for you

644
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:50,510
to keep running to his room.

645
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,590
He's recovered now.

646
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:52,820
Let me see what you've brought.

647
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:56,400
It's all my favorite food.

648
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,350
You are rare here. I'll make some tea,

649
00:30:58,350 --> 00:30:59,350
and let's chat for a while.

650
00:30:59,370 --> 00:31:00,160
-Let's go.
-Wait...

651
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:01,640
Come on, come on.

652
00:31:05,930 --> 00:31:06,690
You asked me to look into

653
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:08,160
Baitou Mountain, and I've got something.

654
00:31:08,540 --> 00:31:09,930
Xie You is quite famous,

655
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,680
which matches what Ji Tanyin said.

656
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:12,720
He once trained two students

657
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:14,480
with high reputations.

658
00:31:14,510 --> 00:31:15,720
One of them is Goddess Wushuang,

659
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,270
who has ascended and is now a god.

660
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:19,400
The other is the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain.

661
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,440
She hasn't ascended,

662
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:22,200
but her reputation among the human race is also quite high.

663
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:23,680
She's the one who took your blow

664
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:25,410
during the Battle of Pinghu.

665
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:29,070
These are the Mute Goddess's

666
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:30,210
three magical treasures—

667
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:32,270
a divine whip that cannot be destroyed,

668
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,030
a phoenix that soars in the sky,

669
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:35,030
and

670
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,750
a treasure bag that can carry all things.

671
00:31:42,320 --> 00:31:43,670
Of course it's true.

672
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:45,270
The doctor said he's recovered.

673
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:46,310
Even if you don't trust me,

674
00:31:46,310 --> 00:31:47,400
don't you trust the doctor?

675
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:49,030
Anyway, don't see him anymore.

676
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:49,920
Just listen to me.

677
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,110
Why can't I see him?

678
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:54,170
Anyway...

679
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,720
Mr. Yuan, you're back?

680
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:58,960
Where have you been?

681
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:04,830
Just wandered around.

682
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:09,200
That painting...

683
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,090
What about it?

684
00:32:14,510 --> 00:32:16,160
I saw a similar one at Pei Jiu's house.

685
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:18,030
The portrait of the Mute Goddess

686
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,320
was also invited here by me,

687
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,880
to pray for Pei Jiu's safety.

688
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:24,790
It seems that the people in this town

689
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:26,760
all believe in the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain.

690
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,640
Of course.

691
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:30,480
When you entered the town,

692
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:32,150
didn't you see the stone at the entrance?

693
00:32:32,310 --> 00:32:33,110
What?

694
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:35,240
This big,

695
00:32:35,640 --> 00:32:36,440
and this tall.

696
00:32:36,610 --> 00:32:37,780
Maybe even taller.

697
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:40,110
It's right at the entrance, with the words "Turn Back" written on it.

698
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,550
Did you not see the Evil-abandoning Tree

699
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:43,480
in the east of the town as well?

700
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:44,630
Does it have words written on it too?

701
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,270
Well, no.

702
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:47,330
Anyway,

703
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:48,680
it's a very large tree.

704
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:49,790
It's said that, back then,

705
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:51,200
37 people sat under that tree,

706
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:51,880
and none of them

707
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,160
were outside the shade.

708
00:32:53,180 --> 00:32:54,620
Can you imagine how big the tree is?

709
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:58,070
Madam, what exactly are you trying to say?

710
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,750
I won't keep you guessing.

711
00:33:00,770 --> 00:33:02,770
What I'm telling you is not just the history of this town,

712
00:33:02,800 --> 00:33:04,120
but also its connection

713
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,620
to the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain.

714
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:06,680
Originally,

715
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,680
this place was a bandit den,

716
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:08,640
called Black Water Stronghold.

717
00:33:08,870 --> 00:33:10,510
As you know, bandits are notorious

718
00:33:10,510 --> 00:33:11,550
for doing all kinds of evil

719
00:33:11,550 --> 00:33:12,640
and wreaking havoc everywhere.

720
00:33:12,660 --> 00:33:13,480
The surrounding villagers

721
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:15,270
had suffered from them for many years.

722
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,230
But these bandits

723
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:17,240
were highly skilled.

724
00:33:17,310 --> 00:33:18,070
Each of the chiefs

725
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:19,070
possessed extraordinary abilities

726
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:20,070
and was ruthless.

727
00:33:20,550 --> 00:33:21,480
For a time,

728
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:23,350
even the authorities had no idea how to deal with them.

729
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,310
And then?

730
00:33:25,110 --> 00:33:27,160
Then, the Mute Goddess of Wu Mountain

731
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,160
stepped in.

732
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:30,000
Upon learning about the bandit problem here,

733
00:33:30,030 --> 00:33:31,550
she came without hesitation

734
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:32,720
to enlighten them.

735
00:33:33,350 --> 00:33:34,160
Enlighten?

736
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,790
There are two kinds of enlightenment—

737
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:37,680
one through kindness, and the other through force.

738
00:33:37,750 --> 00:33:38,550
Kindness

739
00:33:38,550 --> 00:33:39,830
works on good people,

740
00:33:39,830 --> 00:33:40,590
but when facing

741
00:33:40,590 --> 00:33:42,160
evil people who refuse to listen,

742
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:43,200
it all comes down to

743
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,790
whose fist is stronger.

744
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:46,700
So that's what you call enlightening through force.

745
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,720
Exactly. It's said that

746
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:50,200
the Goddess beat them terribly back then.

747
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:50,880
Not only that,

748
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,160
but she dragged them under the tree and lectured them

749
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,680
for three days and three nights

750
00:33:53,920 --> 00:33:55,070
until all 36 chiefs

751
00:33:55,070 --> 00:33:56,880
were fully convinced.

752
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,550
She didn't just defeat them physically—she broke their spirits too?

753
00:33:59,830 --> 00:34:01,110
The Mute Goddess

754
00:34:02,030 --> 00:34:04,030
is truly ruthless.

755
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:04,830
How else

756
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:06,270
can you deal with evildoers without being ruthless?

757
00:34:06,790 --> 00:34:07,780
After that,

758
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,320
the Black Water Stronghold disbanded—

759
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,030
some left,

760
00:34:10,030 --> 00:34:11,030
while some stayed.

761
00:34:11,030 --> 00:34:11,480
But

762
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:12,800
no one committed crimes anymore.

763
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,880
They settled down, married,

764
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:15,480
and lived peaceful lives ever after.

765
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,110
To remember this event

766
00:34:17,110 --> 00:34:18,070
and serve as a warning to future generations,

767
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,030
they erected the Turning Back Stone

768
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:20,280
at the town entrance,

769
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:22,030
symbolizing that it's never too late

770
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,280
for a lost soul to turn back.

771
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:26,000
This event happened hundreds of years ago.

772
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,550
People come and go in this town,

773
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:29,070
and the name "Black Water Stronghold"

774
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:30,480
is almost forgotten by everyone.

775
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,590
Only that stone remains,

776
00:34:31,590 --> 00:34:32,840
standing there without budging.

777
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:35,150
Isn't that a clear testament

778
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:36,710
to the Goddess' achievements?

779
00:34:39,370 --> 00:34:40,600
It certainly is,

780
00:34:40,929 --> 00:34:42,600
and it's very obvious.

781
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:45,630
Even I didn't notice it.

782
00:34:46,139 --> 00:34:48,280
That's why it's only natural

783
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,480
that we honor the Goddess.

784
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:51,000
You've only seen a few households.

785
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:52,110
If you're curious,

786
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:53,159
you can go from house to house,

787
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:54,620
and you can see that every family worships the Goddess.

788
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,110
Is that so?

789
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,800
Looks like the Mute Goddess

790
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,670
is truly a celestial being who descended to the world

791
00:35:01,810 --> 00:35:03,210
to save all beings.

792
00:35:04,110 --> 00:35:04,920
Ji Tanyin,

793
00:35:06,510 --> 00:35:07,440
what do you think?

794
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:13,480
Since that's the case,

795
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:15,320
we absolutely must not

796
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,590
be disrespectful.

797
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:18,630
Madam,

798
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:21,030
could you sell me some incense?

799
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:22,510
I'd like to pay my respects too.

800
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:23,800
Oh, don't be silly.

801
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,440
I don't make money from just anything.

802
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:26,720
If you want to pay respects to the Goddess,

803
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,320
I can't possibly take your money.

804
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:29,960
Please, go ahead.

805
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:50,960
Mute Goddess,

806
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:53,590
I, a mere mortal, Yuanzhong,

807
00:35:53,900 --> 00:35:55,130
am offering incense to you

808
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,280
and praying for your blessings.

809
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,360
Remember to pray for wealth.

810
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:00,670
Praying for wealth is very effective.

811
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:07,400
First, I pray for your protection over me,

812
00:36:08,150 --> 00:36:09,480
to discern loyalty and treachery

813
00:36:10,510 --> 00:36:11,880
when making friends,

814
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:15,880
and not to be deceived by false hypocrites.

815
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:26,630
Second, I pray for you to bless me

816
00:36:26,630 --> 00:36:28,000
with a smooth path in life,

817
00:36:28,270 --> 00:36:29,580
allowing me to come and go freely,

818
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:34,000
and to be free from the traps of hypocrisy and deceit.

819
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:39,150
Third, I pray for you to bless me

820
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,150
with good fortune,

821
00:36:41,670 --> 00:36:43,030
to avoid disasters,

822
00:36:43,320 --> 00:36:46,630
and to keep me safe from all my old and new enemies and foes

823
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:48,440
with honeyed words but evil intentions.

824
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:03,070
Goddess, may you show your divine power.

825
00:37:29,670 --> 00:37:31,280
I am severely injured now

826
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:33,510
and definitely no match for them.

827
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,400
If I want to make it,

828
00:37:36,090 --> 00:37:37,700
I need to wait for the right moment and use wisdom to win.

829
00:38:03,510 --> 00:38:05,400
I, Li Chaoyang, Chief of the War Demons,

830
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,710
greet you, Goddess.

831
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:09,630
Let me ask you,

832
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,800
have the things I entrusted to you

833
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,960
been fully prepared?

834
00:38:16,670 --> 00:38:17,550
Goddess,

835
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:19,480
everything has been prepared

836
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,480
according to your instructions,

837
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:21,880
without any mistakes.

838
00:38:28,630 --> 00:38:30,960
Ji Tanyin is her real name.

839
00:38:31,590 --> 00:38:33,360
Her birth date is on the paper.

840
00:38:33,710 --> 00:38:35,760
Tomorrow is her birthday.

841
00:38:36,950 --> 00:38:38,070
There must be no mistakes.

842
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:39,190
Yes.

843
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,630
Yuanzhong.

844
00:38:47,440 --> 00:38:48,230
Yuanzhong?

845
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:50,150
I made noodles.

846
00:38:50,150 --> 00:38:51,400
Come out and eat with me.

847
00:38:58,710 --> 00:38:59,510
What's wrong?

848
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:01,070
I came to call Yuanzhong for noodles,

849
00:39:01,070 --> 00:39:02,230
but he's not opening the door.

850
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:03,760
He must have gone out.

851
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,320
But I didn't see him leave.

852
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,400
Go and have some rest.

853
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,200
I'll go find him.

854
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:21,280
Yuanzhong, it's me.

855
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:30,030
I knew you were here.

856
00:39:30,190 --> 00:39:31,150
Why didn't you open the door?

857
00:39:31,150 --> 00:39:31,960
I have no appetite.

858
00:39:32,030 --> 00:39:32,680
I'm not hungry.

859
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:34,760
Not hungry?

860
00:39:36,390 --> 00:39:37,920
Is there a big secret

861
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,190
that you can only tell me?

862
00:39:41,110 --> 00:39:42,230
From now on,

863
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,360
everything about me

864
00:39:43,360 --> 00:39:44,320
is a secret,

865
00:39:44,530 --> 00:39:46,010
especially to Ji Tanyin.

866
00:39:46,550 --> 00:39:47,360
Why?

867
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:47,880
Haven't we already known

868
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,360
that something's wrong with her?

869
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,670
But hasn't she already...

870
00:39:51,670 --> 00:39:53,070
She's the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain.

871
00:39:53,590 --> 00:39:54,400
What?

872
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:56,110
How is that possible?

873
00:39:56,230 --> 00:39:57,070
Are you shocked?

874
00:39:57,260 --> 00:39:58,610
I was even more shocked than you are.

875
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,360
I originally thought she was just...

876
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:02,510
I knew there was something wrong with her.

877
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,360
I knew she had ulterior motives.

878
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:05,590
I knew her deliberately approaching

879
00:40:05,590 --> 00:40:06,880
was certainly not with good intentions!

880
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:08,150
I should have realized it earlier.

881
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:09,110
I should have thought of it.

882
00:40:09,110 --> 00:40:10,330
I should have awakened to it sooner!

883
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:11,440
Yuanzhong,

884
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,480
there's no need to be so agitated.

885
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:15,510
Am I agitated?

886
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:16,230
Which one of your eyes

887
00:40:16,230 --> 00:40:17,110
saw me being agitated?

888
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:18,150
I'm happy.

889
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:19,590
I can't be happy enough.

890
00:40:19,610 --> 00:40:20,940
Now that we've exposed her,

891
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:22,320
what should we do next?

892
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:24,920
Indeed,

893
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:26,400
I don't know why

894
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,400
Ji Tanyin appeared

895
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:28,840
by your side either,

896
00:40:29,070 --> 00:40:30,550
but we've been with her for so long—

897
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:33,150
from Fangwai Mountain to the tower ship,

898
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,440
to Baitou Mountain,

899
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:36,440
and now to Orange Lake.

900
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,760
It's been quite a journey.

901
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,710
I don't think she has any ill intentions.

902
00:40:42,510 --> 00:40:43,320
At least,

903
00:40:44,300 --> 00:40:45,970
she's genuinely been protecting you.

904
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:51,280
However,

905
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:54,760
whether she's good or bad,

906
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,840
and no matter what her intentions are,

907
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:57,800
I feel that

908
00:40:58,190 --> 00:40:59,070
she is no longer suitable

909
00:40:59,070 --> 00:41:00,320
to stay by your side.

910
00:41:01,150 --> 00:41:01,960
Because

911
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:04,110
she will disturb your mind,

912
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,230
or perhaps,

913
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:08,030
she already has.

914
00:41:08,360 --> 00:41:10,320
Yuanzhong, this can't go on.

915
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,190
She will interfere

916
00:41:12,190 --> 00:41:13,880
with what we need to do next.

917
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:31,670
Miss Ji.

918
00:41:34,590 --> 00:41:35,590
Have your injuries healed?

919
00:41:37,000 --> 00:41:37,800
Thank you for your concern.

920
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:38,860
It's no longer a problem.

921
00:41:42,670 --> 00:41:43,550
What are you doing?

922
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,840
I'm making a cabinet.

923
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:47,360
The landlady is getting married.

924
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,230
It's a gift for her.

925
00:41:49,510 --> 00:41:50,840
Miss, you're really kind.

926
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:52,110
We're friends, after all.

927
00:41:52,230 --> 00:41:53,030
Friends?

928
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:54,760
I thought

929
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:56,630
you were just guests at the inn.

930
00:41:58,110 --> 00:41:59,110
Can't a guest and the owner

931
00:41:59,150 --> 00:42:00,430
be friends?

932
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:02,320
Of course they can.

933
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:05,230
It's just that most people come and go in a hurry,

934
00:42:05,230 --> 00:42:06,230
just passing by,

935
00:42:06,590 --> 00:42:07,800
making it hard to make true friends.

936
00:42:10,630 --> 00:42:11,440
Miss Ji,

937
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,920
are you planning to stay here for a long time?

938
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:15,000
Why did you come here?

939
00:42:15,550 --> 00:42:17,190
Are you here visiting family and friends...

940
00:42:18,420 --> 00:42:19,230
or just traveling?

941
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:23,920
Miss, please don't get me wrong.

942
00:42:24,260 --> 00:42:25,260
The reason I asked

943
00:42:25,290 --> 00:42:27,930
is because you've covered

944
00:42:27,950 --> 00:42:28,910
many of my expenses.

945
00:42:29,230 --> 00:42:30,800
I don't have any money at the moment,

946
00:42:31,030 --> 00:42:32,470
and I thought if you're planning to stay here for a long time,

947
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,280
it would be easier for me to pay you back.

948
00:42:34,340 --> 00:42:35,490
Is that the reason?

949
00:42:37,170 --> 00:42:39,170
It's fine. You don't need to pay me back.

950
00:42:39,230 --> 00:42:40,070
How could I?

951
00:42:40,320 --> 00:42:41,670
Yuanzhong is very wealthy.

952
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:42,960
Using his money to help you

953
00:42:42,980 --> 00:42:44,360
would probably make him happy too.
